  "text": "In Ref. [CITATION_1] , the authors proposed a promising method for ultrasonic temperature measurement. and the problem of system calibration was also mentioned. In this section, a brief overview is given. The graphic abstract of temperature measurement is shown in Fig 1. If equation C = f(T) represents the inner dependence between the temperature (T) and the ultrasound velocity (C), then T can be determined when C is measured",
